    <span style="font-weight:900; color:Crimson;">
        If you go into negative earnings, the most you can bet is what will get you back
        to your original $1000.
    </span>
    Here's a 'true life' example: Tommy Fike goes into the hole $500. The most he can bet
    the next week is $1500.
    <span style="font-weight:900; color:Crimson; ">
